  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t【这盛世，如你所愿】<br/>\r\n10月23日，此前影响恶劣的虐猫博主“杰克辣条”突然在微博上复出，发长文斥责“假动保”，并称自己热爱小动物。<br/>\r\n同时在自己的网站再次更新了十几条虐猫视频。<br/>\r\n从几个月前人人喊打的虐猫博主如今被捧为“除猫英雄”，不得不感叹“时势造英雄”。<br/>\r\n这盛世，如你所愿！<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMGE3MTA1ZGQ4NDZlN2YzZmViNjRmLmpwZz93aWR0aD01NzImaGVpZ2h0PTExMTU\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0a7105dd846e7f3feb64f.jpg?width=572&amp;height=1115\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0a7105dd846e7f3feb64f.jpg?width=572&amp;height=1115\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0a7105dd846e7f3feb64f.jpg?width=572&amp;height=1115\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZWFkN2JjYWVmZjA0YWYzYzcxNzQyLmpwZz93aWR0aD01NDkmaGVpZ2h0PTk4MA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ead7bcaeff04af3c71742.jpg?width=549&amp;height=980\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ead7bcaeff04af3c71742.jpg?width=549&amp;height=980\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ead7bcaeff04af3c71742.jpg?width=549&amp;height=980\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMzcwNmI3NDJiNjQxYWMwYmVhZWExLmpwZz93aWR0aD03NDkmaGVpZ2h0PTEyMTE\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3706b742b641ac0beaea1.jpg?width=749&amp;height=1211\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3706b742b641ac0beaea1.jpg?width=749&amp;height=1211\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3706b742b641ac0beaea1.jpg?width=749&amp;height=1211\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvODQ3NzI3NjkzYzU4M2FmYmYwYTM5LmpwZz93aWR0aD01NDYmaGVpZ2h0PTEwNTA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/847727693c583afbf0a39.jpg?width=546